		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">武器被夺后，若为女线列军，则进行2次拳击，均造成<span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">武器被夺后，若为男线列军，则抬腿旋转踢，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/线列军.assets/Image_16.png')" x="719" y="842">
